{"tid":100010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2017鄰國封關鎖國趨勢討論","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T06:57:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da2fd13ef51453d4a6835e8ffab0aa64c3321fa4","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"乜o野係封關鎖國? <br />\nPTT和微博都傳緊鄰國會在2017年閉關鎖國."},{"pid":"ceb5a6ca865ca63a028fbf356ef998274daadb4d","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"點鎖法? <br />\n<br />\n要求國民更換新護照,新護照由政府代為保管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> . <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後只有公務人員可以因公務出國. <br />\n<br />\n取消國際航線. <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後只可進口石油和糧食. <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後走唔切的香港人,澳門人和台灣人請自行諗方法逃出鄰國."},{"pid":"e82c1c9e10c6df19d6c8e0238067c6facf71bbd9","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"點解要鎖國? <br />\n<br />\n由於鄰國沒有兌現當年加入WTO的承諾,現時有不少國家對鄰國發起反傾銷訴訟. <br />\n<br />\n現時持續有外資企業撤出鄰國,造成大量藍領和白領失業, <br />\n為遏止失業人口和貧富懸殊造成的社會矛盾及阻止外匯流出, <br />\n鄰國政府決定使用均貧卡,閉關鎖國並重回計劃經濟."},{"pid":"2c69a5743a1014cabfffa89db71c870190d0176c","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾時會鎖國? <br />\n<br />\n現時有3個傳聞日期. <br />\n<br />\n1.今年第十九次全國代表大會（簡稱十九大）閉幕日宣佈鎖國. source: PTT <br />\n<br />\n2.今年十月一日鎖國. source:新浪微博 <br />\n<br />\n3.今年第一季鎖國. source:Facebook"},{"pid":"bc9ebb6a3006777fc9e7708fb1ee2d7ac2be8467","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"鎖國後會發生咩事? <br />\n<br />\n反右2.0 <br />\n<br />\n上山下鄉2.0 <br />\n<br />\n文革2.0"},{"pid":"70bdd7fb0241bc9f57231473d12515e107a9a0fb","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>鎖國前的徵兆 </strong><br />\n<br />\n2017年上半年鄰國發生:股套，匯封，債爆，樓凍，食通天. <br />\n<br />\n股套:A股暴漲然後突然關閉市場,所有股民變蟹民. <br />\n<br />\n匯封:唔俾人換外幣.1月26號外匯管理局發出通知,現在鄰國企業已經受到影響了. <br />\n<br />\n債爆:美國加息,鄰國企業還唔起美元債而違約. <br />\n<br />\n樓凍:今年3月或4月鄰國將推出房產交易稅o黎凍結二手樓宇買賣市場. <br />\n<br />\n食通天:最快下個月開始物價會gogogo! <br />\n<br />\nsource:神棍的twitter和微博."},{"pid":"3d3e06717bf76df636d14c9b266ade0fccdadc99","tid":100010,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514e6386dc659187b0146514f92745f61112a314","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"2017年下半年鄰國鎖國前後的具體重要事項. <br />\n<br />\n可能係7月發生 <br />\n鄰國和美國斷交. <br />\n<br />\n9月或10月 <br />\n十九大閉幕日或國慶日宣佈鎖國."},{"pid":"0e8024d62c6c97a3bb27af080729a7a3d3f8b0bd","tid":100010,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"PTT同微博有無source?"},{"pid":"290bcfb04983adc1725e3de1476901b77da292c9","tid":100010,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點鎖法? <br />\n<br />\n要求國民更換新護照,新護照由政府代為保管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> . <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後只有公務人員可以因公務出國. <br />\n<br />\n取消國際航線. <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後只可進口石油和糧食. <br />\n<br />\n鎖國後走唔切的香港人,澳門人和台灣人請自行諗方法逃出鄰國.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都聽微博講，三月底（第一季之內），支那會取消所有國際航線，制止走資<br />\n<br />\n任何外國人出國都需要申請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa29bd6120ab5cbfa775e0e0920261875b70e484","tid":100010,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PTT同微博有無source?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經比人刪哂，但都係事實"},{"pid":"29ebeb6fa8ca79512b2461e4d069001fe1003f79","tid":100010,"uid":8493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"好似太偏激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ecaa47ecd118262d5db0e4094a47d84aaa428","tid":100010,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>PTT同微博有無source?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經比人刪哂，但都係事實</blockquote><br />\nPTT點會比人刪"},{"pid":"a1c66b70bc69a1cf2aad63364e20ed21380b26a7","tid":100010,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46d2ffc6a01f202ed88d309928442b040ea2839a","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"鎖國後將會發生的事. <br />\n<br />\n2017年10月 <br />\n大學解僱思想或政治不正確的職員. <br />\n<br />\n跟住出現反右2.0,所有機構提供6%人去勞改."},{"pid":"41c3e1404701beb4845ae3e5b04dfce599e37150","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"2017年2月 <br />\n跨境匯款業務，2月1日起取消。 <br />\n(唔肯定係咪指1月26號的外匯管理局通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .) <br />\n<br />\n2017年3月 <br />\n百度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017年4月 <br />\n天涯社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017年7月 <br />\n美國停止進口鄰國商品. <br />\n<br />\n2017年10月 <br />\n新浪微博 <br />\n月底時各大視頻網站要將外國影視作品下架 <br />\n<br />\n2017年11月 <br />\n微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017年12月 <br />\nQQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年 <br />\n停止國民去外國留學,留學生要在2018年回國."},{"pid":"bfb4e162d79561e4dc7fa25fbb5d9cb80df6fe71","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"2017年3月 <br />\n禁止大學職員去外國出席會議 <br />\n<br />\n以下是PTT轉貼的微博<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KOFY1Oa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKOFY1Oa.jpg&h=41aebcec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f110ac69864707ba76e7861a20cadee61be15341","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"以下是截至2017年1月10號的神棍微博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/BiLX1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FBiLX1J.jpg&h=0114d8ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9eff5b199fe9e090ecac91406366bc7b9f415ac","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"今次鎖國鎖幾耐? <br />\n<br />\n神棍:鎖30年 <br />\n劉仲敬twitter:希望2018年8國聯軍再o黎一次"},{"pid":"0d7d50ae9865c96682d02e2a56934808e720d185","tid":100010,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f663997efd5c95d4659a611d5b23155767998099","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:52:38.000Z","msg":"梁振英引述陳家洛在《明報》一篇訪問中說，「我時時在班上挑戰我的學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">問他們有無想過有天早上醒來，五星紅旗升不起，有無想像過歷史重擔要忽然落在他們身上</span>」；<br />\n又引述陳健民本月4日在《明報》撰文，結語中指「我相信中國現時的發展模式是不能持續的，10年間必有大變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，<br />\n梁說雖然文章「無講得好白」，但已清楚顯示有關人士心內想法。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://ppt.cc/o241Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fppt.cc%2Fo241Z&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ce6271ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://ppt.cc/o241Z</a>"},{"pid":"e0fbbba7becdb4b1320f350ffc35ab312b68864c","tid":100010,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"Still don't know whether it's true or not."},{"pid":"3270bc1626b808f4acbcd260b00cc363fcd9deaf","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img 