/>\n聽住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345c2778595b42a6d7da28759483724dd689268f","tid":100010,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"當笑話睇過算啦<br />\n你以為虫國人個個都弱智啦<br />\n平時就係<br />\n去到關自已飯碗事就個個出黎同你博<br />\n呢個就係小農DNA唯一優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff6b45e9814829a3f3ba39d17e8ff22b37db76c","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"朱振華狂舔棍蛋蛋 <br />\n今天 15:37 <br />\n<br />\n中國某位控制了上萬億資產的超級富豪，在農曆大年三十深夜被數十名公安、國安人員抓捕。 <br />\n這名超級財富搡盤手，打理的財富據說達萬億人民幣，涉及多數頂尖的家族。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱振華狂舔棍蛋蛋 <br />\n20分鐘前 <br />\n<br />\n據說這是19祝壽的第一份<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/emimage/ee8492.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.t.sinajs.cn%2Ft4%2Fappstyle%2Fexpression%2Femimage%2Fee8492.png&h=ad78b5e6&s={SIZE}\" />，後面還有更多<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/emimage/ee8492.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.t.sinajs.cn%2Ft4%2Fappstyle%2Fexpression%2Femimage%2Fee8492.png&h=ad78b5e6&s={SIZE}\" />。 ​​​​"},{"pid":"e3881876a71d4e798bc9bea95793585143125c8d","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"以後赴美生子會怎麼樣啊？棍棍 <br />\n今天 15:07 <br />\n<br />\n朱振華狂舔棍棍蛋蛋：斷。<span style=\"color: red;\">但是之前的怎麼處理不知道。 </span><br />\n今天 15:10"},{"pid":"ba4d8daba2e6a18929e30b90ac943f3ead3ee6dc","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"朱振華狂舔棍蛋蛋 <br />\n今天 03:30 <br />\n<br />\n幹活又來了！ ​​​​ <br />\n<img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006C4Csjgy1fc842yiy6xj30k00zkaf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006C4Csjgy1fc842yiy6xj30k00zkaf4.jpg&h=0337e681&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa7a9ee3e3f1e8ea31d975b7e36d4e9a9239c5b9","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442484d62a9b10adbbc8c3db2c8596e15b5d906a","tid":100010,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李丞責:雞年反覆 香港大變局<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n「香港今年的命運，進入了一個新的調整期，中肯地說，是近乎一百八十度的大變，而這個變化期的起點，<span style=\"color: red;\">大致上是出現在年初幾個月，甚至更早。</span>」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/62477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F62477&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4aa4c272\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/62477</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通真係提早到四月鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9c35818be0a74814e00eaee636a14a6c4a3cf5","tid":100010,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"如果鎖國香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ce68b813d35080db223da09a7a33d5ce20e2d1","tid":100010,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果鎖國香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自成一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56e9334f7f3706fa4f2228576bd4ef007e6e10e","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"@連台灣都幹不過（豬都認為大鍋撅起了），會不會引起豬圈的憤怒？野心家倒閣？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>神棍 </strong><br />\n30分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n會引導你恨美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bc650f50c2d5cb6b3b3e0ee83c7de839356131","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"@南海呢，也放棄？這也符合美卿提勒森說法，不讓其進入南海人工島，可是這樣贏國的臉對內往哪放？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>神棍 </strong><br />\n17分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n美帝會盡一切努力維繫他在海外的貿易通道。<span style=\"color: red;\">今後幾十年是沒有中國參與的國際貿易</span>，但這條東南亞代替中國作為廉價商品出口基地的海上通路是必須保住的。<br />\n否則贏國在南海上弄幾個島，不做貿易也可以吃過路費了。一下變成了好幾個新加坡了。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得美帝會允許嗎？在權衡利弊後，一路一帶才被迫成了選項。"},{"pid":"24fad9d009de0cf46428a22f9ecc2c716589c9a1","tid":100010,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"太誇張<br />\n信唔過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，強國有鎖國呢個趨勢<br />\n一步一步措施鎖起來<br />\n<br />\n但你講果d太誇張，而且太快<br />\n信不過"},{"pid":"8430b2e16fd28ed31c39a2e68f038eaa69befc09","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"@南海或釣島，今天美國說了，只要敢動釣島，立刻反擊，絕對履行美日安保條約。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>神棍</strong><br />\n14分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n這個絕對不是開玩笑。美帝確實真的會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n釣魚島本身並不值錢，但是其海域歸屬問題才是重點。<br />\n<br />\n沒有哪艘商船喜歡挨著大朝鮮海岸線走的哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n@看看之後中俄如何反目成仇，也是一樂。一山不能藏二虎。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神棍 <br />\n8分鐘前 <br />\n<br />\n中俄一定會反目。但是唯一發生的條件是老子把兒子榨乾的時候。再無更多油水確認後，將和美歐談合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"95c59b02f666b6883e01b118d1d7fe3a4305e219","tid":100010,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太誇張<br />\n信唔過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，強國有鎖國呢個趨勢<br />\n一步一步措施鎖起來<br />\n<br />\n但你講果d太誇張，而且太快<br />\n信不過</blockquote><br />\nD料好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪唔信，到發生時你會冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e8cb01765a44ef69ce4e0f3a747f871aca11fc","tid":100010,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:04:02.000Z","m