thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F%20i.imgsafe%20.org%2F621b199.gif%20&h=b9c9a55e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49088cf93b7193b96688fc2acc7a2656dbfc4fad","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"長得帥不如跑的快 <br />\n<br />\n外儲在最壞情況下還可以支持15個月就造光了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300108aeb6ff14c8bab14500c3e8431fa09d1c5d","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"grace_xiang <br />\n<br />\n我至今也沒明白，他們為什麼要消耗外儲，死扛匯率，想來想去只有兩個理由：外債和海外收購。。。 <br />\n所以現在黨國只有兩個選擇： <br />\n第一，十天後立刻匯率管制，還能保點家底。 <br />\n第二，把這點外儲全部敗光，十五個月後再管制。 <br />\n<br />\n我賭黨國選第一種做法，大家認為呢？"},{"pid":"6c7b7f0335bb126f65fc269e7161c6bdeb26566a","tid":100010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"grace_xiang <br />\n<br />\n聽說明年全國四六級英語都停考了， <br />\n大家趕緊囤點英語教材吧，可以自己看，最重要的是給孩子用， <br />\n等這三十年漫漫長夜過去後，你的孩子就有可能成為最優秀的人才，才有機會離開這個國家。。。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/732085c2gw1fav2s21egjj20ku112jw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F732085c2gw1fav2s21egjj20ku112jw5.jpg&h=e905b256&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/732085c2gw1fav2rzuyv5j20ku112wjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F732085c2gw1fav2rzuyv5j20ku112wjf.jpg&h=dedfb773&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n12月18日 17:33"}]}